</div>
			<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">Peter Felix Richards</h1>
									<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
									<div id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
								<div id="contentSub"></div>
												<div id="jump-to-nav" class="mw-jump">
					Jump to:					<a href="#mw-head">navigation</a>, 					<a href="#p-search">search</a>
				</div>
				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><p><b>Peter Felix Richards</b> (1808–1868) was a prominent pioneer nineteenth-century Scottish merchant in post-<a href="/wiki/Treaty_of_Nanjing" title="Treaty of Nanjing" class="mw-redirect">Treaty of Nanjing</a> Shanghai, and the founder of the Richards Hotel and Restaurant, the first foreign hotel in China, and the forerunner to the <a href="/wiki/Astor_House,_Shanghai" title="Astor House, Shanghai" class="mw-redirect">Astor House Hotel</a>.</p>
<p></p>
